import React from 'react'
import { Slide } from '../components/Slide/Slide'
import { Category } from '../components/Category/Category'
import {Item} from '../components/Item/Item'
import { Navbar } from '../components/Navbar/Navbar'

export const Home = () => {
  return (
    <>
    <Slide/>
    <Category/>
    <Item/>
    <Navbar/>
    </>
  )
}
